               stealing, on the <rs id="t18310630-136-cd728" type="crimeDate">22nd of June</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310630-136-off727 t18310630-136-cd728"></join>, 1 breast-pin, value 12s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18310630-136-victim1013" type="victimName">
                           Samuel 
                           Hosier
                        <interp inst="t18310630-136-victim1013" type="surname" value="Hosier"></interp>
